datasets.name: 60629a6e
datasets.query:
SELECT *, CASE
    WHEN year_of_death IS NOT NULL THEN FLOOR(DATEDIFF(TO_DATE(year_of_death), TO_DATE(year_of_birth)) / 365)
    ELSE FLOOR(DATEDIFF(CURRENT_DATE(), TO_DATE(year_of_birth)) / 365)
END AS age_in_years
FROM main.dbdemos_aibi_hls_genomics.demographics
where race is NOT NULL

datasets.name: 49313e57
datasets.query:
with umap_embeddings as (
    SELECT *, count(*) over (partition by tissue_or_organ_of_origin) as count 
    FROM main.dbdemos_aibi_hls_genomics.expression_profiles_umap
)
select * from umap_embeddings
where count> 200

datasets.name: c44f1b7d
datasets.query:
WITH exposure_history AS (
    SELECT 
        gender,
        alcohol_history,
        alcohol_intensity,
        cigarettes_per_day,
        COALESCE(years_smoked, 0) AS years_smoked,  -- Replace NULL with 0
        primary_diagnosis,
        COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY primary_diagnosis) AS count_diagnosis
    FROM 
        main.dbdemos_aibi_hls_genomics.exposures
    JOIN 
        main.dbdemos_aibi_hls_genomics.diagnoses
        ON exposures.case_id = diagnoses.case_id
    JOIN 
        main.dbdemos_aibi_hls_genomics.demographics
        ON demographics.case_id = exposures.case_id
    WHERE 
        alcohol_history IS NOT NULL 
        AND cigarettes_per_day IS NOT NULL
) 
SELECT * 
FROM exposure_history
WHERE count_diagnosis > 20;

datasets.name: 4ca282a8
datasets.query:
SELECT *, CASE
    WHEN year_of_death IS NOT NULL THEN FLOOR(DATEDIFF(TO_DATE(year_of_death), TO_DATE(year_of_birth)) / 365)
    ELSE FLOOR(DATEDIFF(CURRENT_DATE(), TO_DATE(year_of_birth)) / 365)
END AS age_in_years
FROM main.dbdemos_aibi_hls_genomics.diagnoses
join main.dbdemos_aibi_hls_genomics.demographics on diagnoses.case_id = demographics.case_id
